  "summaries": [
    "<b>Cobalt Ore</b> is the lowest tier of <linked>Hardmode</linked> <linked>Ore</linked>, and can spawn on the first breaking of an <linked>Altar</linked>. More will spawn on the 4th, 7th, 10th, etc destroyed Altars, albeit in decreasing amounts. Mining Cobalt Ore requires at least a <linked>Molten Pickaxe</linked>. It is immune to all types of explosions.",
    "<linked>Palladium Ore</linked> may generate in place of Cobalt Ore. It is slightly more valuable, and the tools and weapons it crafts have slightly better stats."
